Object: 0x1000 Device Type
Object Code Variable
Description This objects contains the CANopen device type of the device.

Sub 0x00
Name Device Type
Data Type UNSIGNED32
Access ro
Defaultvalue 454
PDO Mapping no

Object: 0x1001 Error Register
Object Code Variable
Description This object contains a register of 8 error information bits.

Sub 0x00
Name Error Register
Data Type UNSIGNED8
Access ro
Defaultvalue 0
PDO Mapping optional, TPDO only

Object: 0x1012 COB ID Time Stamp
Object Code Variable
Description This object shall indicate the configured COB-ID of the Time-Stamp Object (TIME). Further, it defines whether the CANopen device consumes the TIME or whether the CANopen device generates the TIME.

Sub 0x00
Name COB ID Time Stamp
Data Type UNSIGNED32
Access rw
Defaultvalue 0x40000100
PDO Mapping no

Object: 0x1017 Producer Heartbeat Time
Object Code Variable
Description The producer heartbeat time shall indicate the configured cycle time of the heartbeat produced by the device.

The value shall be given in multiples of 1 ms. The value 0 shall disable the producer heartbeat.

Sub 0x00
Name Producer Heartbeat Time
Data Type UNSIGNED16
Access rw
Defaultvalue 0
PDO Mapping no

Object: 0x6105 Battery pack temperatur
Object Code Array
Description This object shall provide the battery pack temperature. As each battery pack may support
several temperature sensors, this object is arranged as an Array, whereby a set of 10h entries
allows administering the measured values of up to 15 temperature sensors. The first entry of
such a set of battery pack-related sensor values shall provide the highest temperature value,
which is currently measured by one of the sensors. The values shall be given in multiples of
0,1 C.

Sub 0x00
Name Highest sub-index supported
Data Type UNSIGNED8
Access ro
Defaultvalue 130
PDO Mapping no

Sub 0x80
Name ET 1 highest temperature value
Data Type INTEGER16
Access rww
PDO Mapping optional

Sub 0x81
Name ET 2 highest temperature value
Data Type INTEGER16
Access rww
PDO Mapping optional

Sub 0x82
Name ET 3 highest temperature value
Data Type INTEGER16
Access rww
PDO Mapping optional

Object Code Array
